<div class="modal fade" id="tli-link-file-modal" tabindex="-1"
     data-search-state="idle"
     data-create-from-url-url="{{ path('app_file_edit-create_from_url') }}?articleId={{ ArticleId }}"
     data-create-from-upload-url="{{ path('app_file_edit-upload_from_modal') }}?articleId={{ ArticleId }}">

    <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-xl">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                    Cerca e inserisci link a file di TurboLab.it
                </h5>
                <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal"></button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">

                <div class="tli-link-file-create-banner mb-3 p-3 border rounded bg-body-tertiary">
                    <p class="small mb-2">
                        Hai cercato e non trovato il file di cui hai bisogno? Puoi crearlo ora.
                        <strong>Carica</strong> il file (Upload) per materiale originale prodotto da te o per file rari/difficili da trovare altrove.
                        <strong>Linka</strong> un URL esterno per file aggiornati frequentemente o facilmente reperibili in rete.
                    </p>
                    <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm tli-link-file-create-via-url" disabled>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i> Crea via URL
                        </button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm tli-link-file-create-via-upload" disabled>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-upload"></i> Crea via Upload
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <p class="small text-muted mt-2 mb-0 tli-link-file-create-hint">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
                        Per evitare duplicati, esegui prima una ricerca.
                    </p>

                    <form class="tli-link-file-create-url-form mt-3 d-none">
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label small mb-1">URL del file</label>
                            <input type="url" class="form-control form-control-sm tli-link-file-url-input"
                                   placeholder="https://esempio.com/file.zip" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label small mb-1">Titolo (nome leggibile)</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm tli-link-file-url-title"
                                   maxlength="{{ constant('App\\Entity\\Cms\\Article::TITLE_MAX_LENGTH') }}" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label small mb-1">Formato</label>
                            <select class="form-select form-select-sm tli-link-file-url-format" required>
                                <option value="">-- scegli --</option>
                                {% for value, Item in Formats %}
                                    <option value="{{ value }}">{% if Item.top %}📌 {% endif %}{{ Item.label|raw }}</option>
                                {% endfor %}
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm tli-link-file-url-submit">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk"></i> Salva e inserisci nell'articolo
                        </button>
                        <div class="tli-link-file-create-error mt-2"></div>
                    </form>

                    <form class="tli-link-file-create-upload-form mt-3 d-none">
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label small mb-1">Seleziona file dal tuo computer</label>
                            <input type="file" class="form-control form-control-sm tli-link-file-upload-input" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-2">
                            <label class="form-label small mb-1">Titolo (nome leggibile)</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-sm tli-link-file-upload-title"
                                   maxlength="{{ constant('App\\Entity\\Cms\\Article::TITLE_MAX_LENGTH') }}" required>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm tli-link-file-upload-submit">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-upload"></i> Carica e inserisci nell'articolo
                        </button>
                        <div class="tli-link-file-create-error mt-2"></div>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <div class="input-group mb-3">
                    <input type="text" class="form-control tli-link-file-search-input"
                           placeholder="Cerca file da linkare...">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary tli-link-file-search-btn" type="button">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i> Cerca
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div class="mb-3 small">
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline me-0">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="tli-link-file-mine-only" name="only-mine" value="1">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="tli-link-file-mine-only">Inseriti da me</label>
                    </div>
                    <span class="border-start mx-2"></span>
                    <span class="me-2">Ordina per:</span>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="file-sort" id="tli-link-file-sort-relevance" value="relevance">
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="tli-link-file-sort-relevance">Rilevanza</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-check form-check-inline">
                        <input class="form-check-input" type="radio" name="file-sort" id="tli-link-file-sort-date" value="date" checked>
                        <label class="form-check-label" for="tli-link-file-sort-date">Data ultimo aggiornamento</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="tli-link-file-results"></div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>
